## Documentation
When making code changes, update related documentation as needed.

## Prompt.AI
This repository is the template source. Keep tracked template files clean.

After each meaningful task:
- Do not append project/session history to `prompt.ai/development_log.md`
- Prefer writing guidance and findings in `prompt.ai/research/`
- If temporary local notes are needed, use `prompt.ai/session_notes.local.md` (gitignored)
- In downstream project repos, update this rule to enable `development_log.md` entries
- For releases, create `prompt.ai/vX.Y.Z_release_summary.md`
